<lb ed="I" n="0083a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>法義兄弟等二百人造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan><cb:div>
<pb n="0084a" xml:id="I01.0033.0084a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0084a01"/><p xml:id="pI01p0084a0101" cb:type="pre">
<lb ed="I" n="0084a02"/>維大魏永熙三年歲次□□□三
<lb ed="I" n="0084a03"/>月癸未朔五日丁<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">亥</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0084a04"/>夫大覺遷方。託靈<note n="0084001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30585"/>＝像【史】</note><note n="0084001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30585"/>【佛拓】，像【史】</note><app n="0084001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">像</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30585"/></rdg></app>以□福。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">法</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">雖</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0084a05"/>謝世。寄三乘以存教。自非遠鑒幽
<lb ed="I" n="0084a06"/>源。寧能<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"><note n="0084002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30356"/>＝辨【史】</note><note n="0084002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30356"/>【佛拓】，辨【史】</note><app n="0084002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">辨</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30356"/></rdg></app></unclear>其由。是以法義兄弟二
<lb ed="I" n="0084a07"/>百人等。識攬玄宗。敬<note n="0084003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𥮵＝崇【史】</note><note n="0084003" resp="ihp" type="mod">𥮵【佛拓】，崇【史】</note><app n="0084003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">崇</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">𥮵</rdg></app><note n="0084004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30401"/>＝正【史】</note><note n="0084004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30401"/>【佛拓】，正【史】</note><app n="0084004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">正</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30401"/></rdg></app>法。減<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">割</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0084a08"/>家財。仰為皇帝　陛下。令為七世
<lb ed="I" n="0084a09"/>父母。營造<note n="0084005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30525"/>＝微【史】</note><note n="0084005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30525"/>【佛拓】，微【史】</note><app n="0084005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">微</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30525"/></rdg></app>福。始訪石孤巖。<note n="0084006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𤩆＝瑍【史】</note><note n="0084006" resp="ihp" type="mod">𤩆【佛拓】，瑍【史】</note><app n="0084006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瑍</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">𤩆</rdg></app>珍
<lb ed="I" n="0084a10"/>玄豁。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">采</unclear>□妙手。敬造尊<app type="star" corresp="#0084001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">像</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30585"/></rdg></app>一區。二
<lb ed="I" n="0084a11"/>侍菩薩。嚴姿超絕。色<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">精</unclear>琨寶。光拂
<lb ed="I" n="0084a12"/>紫虛。暉洞皎日。崇髣髴於幽蹤。依
<lb ed="I" n="0084a13"/>悕於聖容者也。緣□微因。願令亡
<lb ed="I" n="0084a14"/>者遊神西方淨佛國土。現存同福
<lb ed="I" n="0084a15"/>長<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">保</unclear>遐□。一切　群生。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">共</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">沐</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">澤</unclear>。</p></cb:div><cb:div>
